or a given set of parameters.\nOur predicted brightness temperatures are proportional to the square of the\nnumber of particles and scale by the inverse five-third power of the azimuthal\nwavenumber which is in rough accord with the observed spectra of radio pulsars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Sep 2004 18:13:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Mar 2005 22:57:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
